    </div><div class="gen_header_central_cell" style="flex-grow:4; text-align:center;"><span class="gen_header_title"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Pedoman gaya</span></span></div><div class="gen_header_forelink searchaux" style="flex-grow:1; justify-content: flex-end; display:flex; align-items:center; text-align:right;"> 
